%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
## InputColor element
We added new input element to the standard library:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Module[{col = {1,0,0}},
  {
    EventHandler[InputColor[col], (col=#)&],
    Graphics[{
      RGBColor[col//Offload], 
      Triangle[],
      RGBColor[({1,1,1}-col)//Offload],
      Disk[{0,0},0.2]
    }]
  } // Column 
]

